public interface SqlServerKey
extends HasId, HasInner<com.microsoft.azure.management.sql.implementation.ServerKeyInner>, HasName, HasResourceGroup, Indexable, Refreshable<SqlServerKey>, Updatable<SqlServerKey.Update>
